flowRoot.flowPara: Open lightweight tools for safe and efficient data management, processing and validation
Store Data Securely; Publish and Collaborate with Ease
Organize and Store Data and Metadata

text.tspan: Maintaining reproducible data workflows while keeping data in sync, backed up, and easily accessible from within and outside
the lab is a key challenge in research. To minimize time and effort invested in these tasks scientists have to spend on these tasks,
we provide a suite of tools designed for comprehensive, reproducible and versioned management of scientific data.
